name: PlanetTest
description: Unit tests for the Planet class, focusing on metadata retrieval for various planets.

test_cases.name: shouldHaveNinePlanets
test_cases.description: Tests if the PlanetName enum has exactly 9 entries and if the planet.yml file contains 9 names.

test_cases.name: shouldReturnCorrectJupiterMetadata
test_cases.description: Tests the metadata retrieval for Jupiter, including length of day, mean distance from the Sun, equatorial gravity, mass, and equatorial radius.
